headline: EA and Full Circle Launch skate. in Early Access Today
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., September 16, 2025--Electronic Arts Inc. (NASDAQ: EA) and Full Circle’s skate., the next chapter in the award-winning skateboarding franchise, releases in Early Access today on PlayStation® 5, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation® 4, Xbox One, PC via Steam, Epic Games Store and EA App. The game is free-to-play*, fully cross-platform with cross-progression support**, making it easy for both longtime fans and new skaters to jump in and ride together. skate.’s Early Access is just the
